}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This device can safely be assumed to be a [[Tenda N6]]. The FCC ID of the N6 has been assigned to this device. :The device is presumed to have 8MB Flash (FW provided by '''Anker''' is ~5MB) and 64MB of RAM like the N6 is shown as having in it's FCC docs..
The default settings are from the [http://www.ianker.com/service/download/c38 manual provided by Anker].
